{"lemma":"عَمَلَةٍ","slug":"عَمَلَةٍ","root":"ع.م.ل","root_slug":"ع-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عامِل","root":"عمل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":12},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":14},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n30575","n30576","n30577","n30578","n30586"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to do business with","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to act in common with"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to treat (in such and such a way)","tags":["transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"عَامِلِ الْكُلَّ بِإِحْسَانٍ تُحَبْ / فَقَدِيمًا جَمَّلَ الْمَرْءَ الْأَدَبْ","english":"Miscellany"}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active, effective"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"factor, constituent, element, causative agent"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"factor (e.g. 6 is a factor of 24)","examples":[{"text":"اَلْعَامِل الْمُشْتَرَك الْأَكْبَر","english":"The highest common factor"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"motive power"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a word that governs the grammatical state of one or more words"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"worker, workman, laborer"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"wage earner, employee"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"maker, producer, manufacturer"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"perpetrator, doer, author"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"governor, lieutenant, vicegerent"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"administrative officer, prefect, district president"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare عَمِلَ (ʕamila, “to do, to work”).\n\nDerived from the active participle of عَمِلَ (ʕamila, “to do, to act, to work”)."},"ipa":["/ʕaː.ma.la/","/ʕaː.mil/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n30575","headword_ar":"عَمْلَةٌ","root":"Eml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Theft:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"treachery, perfidy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unfaithfulness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) it is not used otherwise than in relation to evil. (O.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n30576","headword_ar":"عُمْلَةٌ","root":"Eml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumaAlapN","text_ar":"عُمَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n30577","headword_ar":"عِمْلَةٌ","root":"Eml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of work, labour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"service;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acting;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of making."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN xabiyvu AlEimolapi","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ خَبِيثُ العِمْلَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupt, in respect of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the mode of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamilapN","text_ar":"عَمِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EumaAlapN","text_ar":"عُمَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"internal state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, of a man, in relation to evil."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n30578","headword_ar":"عَمِلَةٌ","root":"Eml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":", is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamalN","text_ar":"عَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A deed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an action"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (O, K:) so in the saying of a woman of the Arabs,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA kaAna liY","text_ar":"مَا كَانَ لِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EamilapN A_il~aA fasaAdukumo","text_ar":"عَمِلَةٌ اـِلَّا فَسَادُكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There was no deed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"action, for me, except the corrupting of you"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that is done,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"performed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is made;"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Eumila","text_ar":"مَا عُمِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EimolpN","text_ar":"عِمْلةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n30586","headword_ar":"عُمَّلَةٌ","root":"Eml","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%84/","headword_ar":"عامل","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23401#0f7f95","body_html":"<span>ما أضمر عامله على شريطة التفسير: هو كل اسم بعده فعل أو شبهة، مشتغل عنه بضمير أو متعلقه لو سلط عليه هو أو ما ناسبه لنصبه، مثل: زيدا ضربته.</span>"},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23401#36d713","body_html":"<span>العامل: ما أوجب كون آخر الكلمة على وجه مخصوص من الإعراب.<br></span><br>العامل القياسي: هو ما صح أن يقال فيه: كل ما كان كذا فإنه يعمل كذا، كقولنا: غلام زيد، لما رأيت أثر الأول في الثاني وعرفت علته قست عليه: ضرب زيد، وثوب بكر.<br><br>العامل السماعي: هو ما صح أن يقال فيه: هذا يعمل كذا وهذا يعمل كذا، وليس لك أن تتجاوز، كقولنا: إن \"الباء\" تجر، و\"لم\" تجزم، وغيرهما.<br><br><div>العامل المعنوي: هو الذي لا يكون للسان فيه حظ، وإنما هو معنى يعرف بالقلب.</div>"}]}}